Please try the following updated code:

```
function simulateTyping() {
  var textInput = document.querySelector('[aria-label="Message @"]');
  if (textInput) {
    var lastChar = textInput.textContent.slice(-1);
    textInput.focus();
    textInput.textContent = textInput.textContent + lastChar;
    textInput.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true }));
  }
}

setInterval(simulateTyping, 2000);
```

This code simulates typing in the Discord app by finding the message input field using the `aria-label` attribute, and then appending the last typed character to the end of the input field, triggering an input event. The time interval is set to 2000 milliseconds (2 seconds), which you can adjust to suit your needs.

